parameters.name: query
parameters.value:
SELECT person.public_id
    FROM pkbperson AS person
    INNER JOIN personcontact AS pc ON person.id = pc.person_id
    WHERE
        pc.contactvalue = 'indepedent.professional@pro.test'

Patients Know Best Help Team
